Description: Graphical tool for managing xgamma command
 xgamma GUI Tool provides a simple, minimalist interface for adjusting
 gamma correction via xgamma command.
 .
 Individual channel control (Red, Green, Blue), real-time preview with
 reference pattern, and autostart support.